org.lindbergframework.persistence.configuration
Class AbstractLinpConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  org.lindbergframework.core.configuration.ConfigurationRepository
      org.lindbergframework.persistence.configuration.AbstractLinpConfiguration
All Implemented Interfaces:
Configuration, LinpConfiguration
Direct Known Subclasses:
SimpleLinpConfiguration, XmlLinpConfiguration
public abstract class AbstractLinpConfiguration
extends ConfigurationRepository
implements LinpConfiguration

abstract lindberg persistence configuration base for linp configuration implementations. This configuration base uses extends ConfigurationRepository to do cache of property configurations.

Author:
Victor Lindberg
